4-84 with 3:41 to play.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joel Embiid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7294066497235516e-27, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the States\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-point play\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Curry rattled in a three-pointer with 2:24 remaining to give the United States their first lead since the first quarter 87-87.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0426275178741315e-16, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Curry\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-pointer\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"their first lead\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 844}, {\"ngram\": \"the first quarter\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James followed with a driving layup, Curry grabbed a steal and drove for a basket that pushed the US lead to five and the Americans held on.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\"